#: C/balsa.xml:4637(para)
msgid ""
"First, create the IMAP folder as you want it configured. Then, press right "
"mouse button on the mailbox entry and select <guimenuitem>Mark as Inbox</"
"guimenuitem>. That is all!"
msgstr ""

